and an episode of rescue 911 broadcast during a 68minute rain 
delay in the seventh inning 
the game averaged an 185 rating and a 33 share according to 
ratings released tuesday by the ac nielsen co a rating point 
represents 921000 households a share is the percentage of all tv 
sets in use tuned to a show in its time period 
