<TEXT>
the worst of times could be the best of times for 
jim gall and his auctioneers 
with the nations savings and loan system in shambles and 
regulators anxious to unload seized assets gall says his 
11yearold auction house is poised for profits and fame 
im as upset about the sampl crisis as anyone were all in for 
